Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://www.postman.com/product/mcp-server/

Package: postman-mcp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Postman MCP server (Model Context Protocol server for the Postman API)
 Model Context Protocol server that lets AI tools and assistants operate on the
 Postman API: collections, workspaces, environments, and API specifications. The
 Node.js runtime is supplied by the consuming image; this package ships the
 compiled server and its production node_modules under /usr/lib/nodejs/postman-mcp.
